snippet.title: AI2U: With You 'Til The End – Steam Early Access Release Trailer
snippet.description:
The iconic yandere AI catgirl, Eddie, alongside the AI witch, Elysia, and your AI assistant, Estelle, have finally made their way to Steam in Early Access with plenty of new features, areas, and customizations!

AI2U: With You 'Til The End features a roster of NPCs who will do anything to keep you by their side. The enchanting witch, Elysia, will always open her door for you, while Estelle, the stunning AI assistant, is programmed to keep you from getting hurt. Do you trust any of these pretty girls to keep you safe in their peculiar abodes, or will you plot your escape?

Your FOREVER begins today, senpai~ 💖🔪

🚂 Buy AI2U on Steam now!: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2880730/AI2U_With_You_Til_The_End/

Follow your yandere AI girlfriends everywhere! They know where to find you if you don't~ 💖🔪
https://www.discord.gg/TZCr3Vqggk 
https://www.instagram.com/ai2u_game/
https://www.twitter.com/ai2u_game
 www.patreon.com/withYouTilTheEnd
